Definition: form a mental image of something that is not present or that is not the case
Example: Can you conceive of him as the president?
Synonyms: adj, all, creative, imaginative, noun, cognition, imagination, conceive_of, ideate, idea, ideation, envisage, create_by_mental_act, form, a, mental, image, of, something, that, is, not, present, or, the, case, Can, you, conceive, him, as, president
Frame: 8,26
Category: verb.creation
